results.title: Live | Laugh | Love Patch  Iron on diy decal for T-shirt, Hoodie, Tank Top, Or any Fabric, Iron on transfer for Fabric, Heat Transfer
results.description:
INSTRUCTIONS

Tools: Ironing Pad, Electric Iron (TURN OFF STEAM) OR Heat Transfer Machine, Sticker Paper

Steps:

1. Place clothes flat on the ironing pad.
2. Put the pattern in the position you want.
3. Make sure steam is off, and the temperature is between 120-160 degree.
4. Iron over the thermal patch for 10-15 seconds with iron.
4. While still hot peel off the clear plastic membrane immediately.
5. If the patch is not flat and intact, repeat step 4.
6. Congratulations pattern is complete.
